com.tiger.commands

Interface LLCommandFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LLRailRoadServiceCommandFactory

    public interface LLCommandFactory
    Interface that defines which functionality an LLCommand factory must provide. The LLCommandFactory provides functionality for creating new commands that implement the LLCommand interface.
